  "title": "SITE SUPERVISOR",
  "description": "<p>Site Supervisor</p><p>- Supervise site electrical installation.</p><p>- Confirm progress reports, monitor project activities</p><p>- Verify works done by workers</p><p>- Receive and confirm client’s instructions of variation works</p><p>- Raise purchase requisition</p><p>- Liaise with Project Manager</p><p>- Prepare documents for electrical testing</p><p>- Rectify and repair electrical issues at site</p><p>- Prepare and submit tender quotations</p><p>- Submit progress claims, monitor project activities</p><p>- Project planning, execute resource management and control</p><p>- Co-ordinate with sub-contractors, suppliers and Consultants for Building Construction Electrical Works</p><p>- Arrange and monitor work progress</p><p>- Monitor project costing to ensure project to be completed within budget and on time delivery<br /></p><p>Requirements:</p><p>- ITE Certificate/Diploma/Degree in Electrical/Civil engineering or Equivalent</p><p>- At least 2 years experience in project supervision/electrical contracting</p>",
